data.description: WONDERFUL home on a beautiful street in highly sought after Ellerbe Road Estates! This 3br 2ba will meet all of your needs, including neutral paint, hardwood floors, and granite countertops throughout! This spacious home features oversized bedrooms, formal dining room, & added walk-in pantry! The fully fenced back yard with large covered patio is very private and great for kids and entertaining! Separate shed with electricity and dog run. Home is wheelchair accessible with plenty of space! Book your showing today!
